; org_backward_overlap.a
; Goal:
;   Determine whether oracle LCC permits .org to move the location counter
;   backwards or into already-defined memory.
; Questions:
;   - Is backward .org rejected?
;   - If rejected, what error text appears?
;   - If accepted, how does the resulting output look?

        .word 1
        .word 2
        .org 1
        .word 3
        halt
